{"tid":9972,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[筲箕灣撚］有咩係必食？！","createTime":"2016-11-28T18:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T16:49:46.000Z","uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"916ef70e4473472203a7c943eb748b9a50d8e010","tid":9972,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"每個星期都總有日要落筲箕灣，但又唔係自己住開 有無人介紹下有咩好食 個邊我最多都只係識落番西灣河食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8246f02530b35f047a8f8ac71c13942461ac130c","tid":9972,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:39:58.000Z","msg":"家住筲箕灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣真係好多好嘢食，<br />\n東大街果頭已經好多，<br />\n不過Sorry巴打我食嘢唔記舖名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說近巴士總站馬路對面有間隱世高人級外賣魚生果D，<br />\n價錢算平但係料靚手工好，款又多，<br />\n夜左返屋企一定行去果度睇下有無靚嘢執<br />\n同埋個老闆真係好撚Cool，未見過佢笑過 <br />\n<br />\n上google睇仲係舊相見唔到間舖，<br />\n好似係南安街7號附近，得一間你實見到"},{"pid":"f28114d77e5caed3ffe42b16aaea8c0870ca68fd","tid":9972,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"好 下個星期望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我見成條東大街都係冰室同茶餐廳 有係邊間比較特別/好食 小弟幾鐘意食茶記野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bb50332dbd2f4ed083eb2abac5733d2755dbf4","tid":9972,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"麗姐  <br />\n<br />\n西灣河狗食咁多 你唔係講去太安樓食垃圾下化"},{"pid":"76d14adc92a13e9f33a7666279d1b154696615b2","tid":9972,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好 下個星期望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我見成條東大街都係冰室同茶餐廳 有係邊間比較特別/好食 小弟幾鐘意食茶記野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果間無堂食的"},{"pid":"16a3e859f27a80e484de2803f99e8ca224dd7956","tid":9972,"uid":13295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"行遠少少去百利<br />\n蕃茄肥牛湯烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5e4df89939613f11ffedba192976b34f15e35a","tid":9972,"uid":11381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:41:37.000Z","msg":"西灣河 華記蛋包飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38c53b0acca1dea19c6353f3e29d079a9392123","tid":9972,"uid":33286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"印尼沙爹屋"},{"pid":"752e611e0b90778b6b00e4e35969bcece67662ec","tid":9972,"uid":40336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"低調高手，印尼沙嗲屋"},{"pid":"a6dc8052b0488bf35a2e7f15cc5b31e39d1854d1","tid":9972,"uid":9170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"川婆婆<br />\n新翠雅"},{"pid":"e74a5d5bbf3a9d829b875883d3ea669d8bbf6780","tid":9972,"uid":32338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"韓食媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e3b341d5db580d7ea8f82e88381d3c1b90c91","tid":9972,"uid":10038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓食媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢間好味"},{"pid":"c19ed07a63573b2a8a33b3279f37214496b5aa9b","tid":9972,"uid":1645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"冠泰<br />\n愛秩序灣街市紹華<br />\n南駅<br />\n東橋"},{"pid":"6c20ada9578756570769f7d6ec340453f550676b","tid":9972,"uid":12127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:47:27.000Z","m